data.description: Fantastic Single Story Home in West Lancaster on a Quiet Cul-de-sac. This home offers 4 spacious bedrooms and 2 full bathrooms. The Primary bathroom has been upgraded with a beautiful stone walk in shower. The kitchen, dining room, and living room have an open and spacious layout. The home is on a quarter acre lot with 2 paved RV access entries that are perfect for all your toys. There is a 2 car garage, and storage room that is perfect for a small workshop space. This home is located close to freeway access and all your shopping needs. Call for your appointment today, YOU ARE GOING TO LOVE IT!
